LL / 17.2.2013

Development scripts to HITChip-QIIME conversions & benchmarking.

The scripts additional (confidential) metadata files. See the script
comments for details.

* Converting HITChip data in QIIME format
  - HITChip2QIIME.sh (main script R + QIIME parts)
  - generatefiles.R (R part; called from the main script)

* Convert various HITChip preprocessing into QIIME format in batch to
  run automated benchmarkings: HITChip2QIIME.R this calls further
  scripts, including
  - generate.qiime.files.R (R + QIIME scripts run from within R)
  - funcs.R (functions)


